{"tid":1085372,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱睇完新戲劇之王","createTime":"2019-03-31T06:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T06:38:04.000Z","uid":129013,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"190a1a98029e47616b04b35b5399a4a7c2c0763b","tid":1085372,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完新戲劇之王我想講周星馳今次想拍嘅嘢都好多意思。其中一個重點一定係拍出咗人性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺全中國都喺度打飛機講自己好好嘅時候，星爺夠膽將中國人嗰種狗眼看人低 利字行先 無理取鬧 仆街冚家產嘅&quot;中國式人性&rdquo;完美展現咗出嚟。其中馬老師呢個角色係發揮得最好嘅，有睇都知佢前面有幾克人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以都好難怪點解大陸票房唔賣帳，佢地睇慣充滿靚仔靚女嘅打飛機電影，要佢地睇返d貼地戲只會令佢地睇到自己平時係點，仲要再醜化多幾分。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒，放低有色眼鏡去睇呢套戲其實幾好睇。"},{"pid":"aef139069c59c9b2c3b3cf5b5f1d41eb0e5ebb0d","tid":1085372,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"屌你係我分身黎？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375338eaa4ef851683aeff7c1519025cb47ddf43","tid":1085372,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F66T7tC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF66T7tC.png&h=85c5c1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cef3e4979ca06d08268d8eff6af4e89e9dc679","tid":1085372,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375338eaa4ef851683aeff7c1519025cb47ddf43","tid":1085372,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1